  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Had to Be Saved</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>They came to solution when you drowned</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>Responsibility's heavy so it went and went around.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>Asked how long the pain will last,</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>Oh memory was a cruel fate, that left marks from the past.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>Who will step and take the blame?</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="6" type="stanza">
          <l>Who will say that you had to be saved?</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="7" type="stanza">
          <l>Who will step and take the blame?</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="8" type="stanza">
          <l>You have an opinion of your own,</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="9" type="stanza">
          <l>Pretend to be one of them,</l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="10" type="stanza">
          <l>Because the thought of being alone...</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="11" type="stanza">
          <l>Waited a while now for a spark,</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="12" type="stanza">
          <l>Lit up the last match and went into the dark.</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
